templateAssets.content: General Education courses are recommended, but not required, to support the student in this major. See Group 1: Recommended General Education Courses, for the selection of courses.
The BA in Geography - Landscape Studies Option is an approved match to the AA-T in Geography.

In sections below where the student is directed to select courses and there is a note "Only lower division courses listed," upper division courses are also available. See the University Catalog for the full listing of degree requirements.
All courses within the Landscape Studies Option are at the upper division level. See the University Catalog for a full listing of degree requirements.
